        <updateDate>2009-01-08T21:56:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Retirement Account Distribution Improvement Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to suspend in 2008, 2009, and 2010 requirements for minimum distributions from tax-deferred retirement plans. Permits taxpayers who have already received a minimum distribution in 2008 to recontribute such distribution to their retirement plans by July 1, 2009.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
